description.en:
What is the project about?

$SPONGE is a complete community driven meme coin. No presale. Zero taxes. Max liquidity.

61% Circulating Supply
29% Community Wallet Locked
10% For CEX Listings
Stealth Launch
DEX Liquidity Locked
Contract Renounced
No. 1 Wallet Locked
No Presale
No Taxes

What makes your project unique?

community wallet locked 
contract renounced

History of your project.

launched 4th may 2023. nearly 10k holders with nearly 100mil market cap peak already

What’s next for your project?

increase holders 
trust wallet listing
more CEX listings 

What can your token be used for?

pure meme coin fun and community
